    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Labels, often having an adhesive backing, bearing the name and address of the intended recipient of mail or packages, to facilitate the dispatch of the items by a postal service or other delivery agent.</Note_Text>
